text:
Prakash Neupane (born March 25, 1997) is a Nepalese rapper. He Started rapping when he was 16 years old. He has written articles for “Thrive Global” & news writer of “Bolchha Nepal”.
Musical career.
Prakash Neupane is a Nepali HiphHop and R&B Artist and Music Composer. He also writes lyrics himself. He has various hit songs like "Aaideuna","Sunana", “Lagcha Maya Timro" “U Got Me”, "Parkhi Baschu", "Rajkumari"(2017), "Kanchi" (2017), "Bang Bang" (2017), "Timro Woripari"(2017) etc. He has released more than 20 songs till now including three albums. He has recently released his new album "Fusion"
